rvice` 依赖 `productcatalogservice`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"productcatalogservice->tidb\", \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\", \"frontend->checkoutservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"作为最下游服务，productcatalogservice的GetProduct操作延迟从10.3ms激增至938ms（91倍），所有三个实例都出现严重延迟，表明这是问题根源\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"虽然trace数据未直接显示tidb调用，但productcatalogservice依赖TiDB存储层，其严重延迟与Metric专家发现的region_pending异常（149.76%增加）一致，表明存储层问题是根本原因\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析结论**：\n- Trace数据确认了`productcatalogservice`是调用链中最下游的异常组件\n- 但考虑到系统拓扑，`productcatalogservice`依赖TiDB存储层\n- Metric专家发现的`region_pending`异常（149.76%增加）与`productcatalogservice`的严重延迟时间上吻合\n- 因此，我支持**tidb-tikv是根本原因**的假设，`productcatalogservice`的延迟是存储层问题的直接表现\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nDISAGREED", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "tidb-tikv is the root cause due to region_pending metric anomaly (149.76% increase)", "current_task_instruction": "当前处于【分析阶段】。\n以下是你可以访问的全量上下文信息，包含了用户输入、当前假设、以及其他所有智能体的历史发现：\n================================\nUUID: 9ee6b9ce-377\n\nUser Query: A fault occurred from 2025-06-19T10:10:24Z to 2025-06-19T10:15:24Z. Please identify the root cause.\n\n\n[RAW DATA CONTEXT]\n\n--- Raw Log Data ---\nNot collected yet\n\n--- Raw Metric Data ---\n{'status': 'success', 'message': '成功加载metric数据。UUID: 9ee6b9ce-377', 'anomaly_metrics': 'metric_type,service_name,pod_name,node_name,metric_name,normal_median,fault_median,normal_p99,fault_p99,median_change_ratio,p99_change_ratio\\nservice,adservice,adservice-2,N/A,client_error_ratio,0.0,0.0,0.48,0.0,0.0,2.0\\nservice,adservice,adservice-2,N/A,error_ratio,0.0,0.0,0.48,0.0,0.0,2.